snippet.title: [New Game] Spider RotL PV
snippet.description:
Spider RotL now available on G123!
In this game based on the popular anime, players can raise and train Kumoko, who has been reincarnated as a spider, and battle powerful monsters in the dungeon with their allies. Enjoy the world of the anime in your browser!

Start playing here: https://s.g123.jp/6pbmv4y5

Start your adventure as Small Lesser Taratect and aim for the top of the evolution tree as Arachne!

■Game Info
Title: Spider RotL
Genre: Dungeon RPG
Price: Free-to-play (in-game purchases available)

#SpiderRotL #SoImASpider #G123
